text: Ahmed Almukhtar (born February 19, 1993) is a Saudi Arabian professional basketball player. He currently plays for Uhud Medina of the Saudi Premier League. He represented Saudi Arabia's national basketball team at the 2017 Arab Nations Basketball Championship in Egypt.
